*nm-applet-0.6.5 (02 May 2007)

  02 May 2007; Steev Klimaszewski <steev@gentoo.org>
  +files/nm-applet-0.6.5-confchanges.patch, +metadata.xml,
  +nm-applet-0.6.5.ebuild:
